ntent via shortlinks.'=>'Gba awọn alejo ti ko wọle laaye lati wo akoonu atunṣe nipasẹ awọn ọna asopọ kuru.','By default, PublishPress Revisions blocks visitors from viewing revision previews. When enabled, revision shortlinks will render the revision content directly for logged-out visitors instead of redirecting to the preview URL.'=>'Nipa aiyipada, awọn atunṣe PublishPress n dènà awọn alejo lati wo awọn awotẹlẹ atunṣe. Nigbati o ba mu ṣiṣẹ, awọn shortlinks atunṣe yoo fi akoonu atunṣe han taara fun awọn alejo ti ko forukọsilẹ dipo ki o tọka si URL awotẹlẹ.','Dummy'=>'Dummy','No post types configured yet. Click "Add Post Type" to get started.'=>'Kò sí iru ifiweranṣẹ ti a ti ṣeto sibẹ. Tẹ "Ṣafikun Iru Ifiweranṣẹ" láti bẹ̀rẹ̀.','Add Post Type'=>'Fi Iru Ifiweranṣẹ Kun','Log entry deleted successfully.'=>'Iwọle log ti parẹ ni aṣeyọri.','%d log entries deleted successfully.'=>'%d awọn akọsilẹ log ti paarẹ ni aṣeyọri.','All logs have been cleared.'=>'Gbogbo awọn iwe ti wa ni mimọ.','Title'=>'Akole','Details'=>'Alaye','Are you sure you want to delete this log entry?'=>'Ṣé o dájú pé o fẹ́ paarẹ́ ifiweranṣẹ yii?','Tablet'=>'Tabulẹti','Mobile'=>'Mobaili','Desktop'=>'Kọmputa','%1$s from %2$s visited at %3$s'=>'%1$s lati %2$s ṣabẹwo ni %3$s','%1$s visited at %2$s'=>'%1$s ṣabẹwo ni %2$s','From %1$s, visited at %2$s'=>'Lati %1$s, ṣabẹwo ni %2$s','Visited at %s'=>'Ti a ṣabẹwo ni %s','via %s'=>'nipasẹ %s','Edit shortlink settings'=>'Ṣatunkọ eto ọna asopọ kukuru','Target url not found.'=>'URL ibi-afẹ́ kò rí.','Invalid URL scheme. Only http, https, ftp, ftps, and mailto are allowed.'=>'Ilana URL ti ko tọ. Nikan http, https, ftp, ftps, ati mailto ni a gba laaye.','Invalid URL.'=>'URL ti ko tọ.','Tiny slug could not created.'=>'Kò le ṣẹda slug kekere.','Link - %s'=>'Ọna asopọ - %s','Shortlink will appear here'=>'Ọna asopọ kukuru yoo farahan nibi','Enter a long URL and make a shortlink'=>'Tẹ URL gigun kan ki o ṣẹda ọna asopọ kukuru','Long URL'=>'URL Gigun','Close'=>'Pa','Create Shortlin